title: Pilates Reformer Workout | 30 min | Full Body
description:
This quick, but intense Pilates reformer workout will give you a full body burn in just 30 min. Perfect for when you're short on time. (extra emphasis on upper body and shoulders)
Hope you enjoy!  

Reformer Bundle - https://amzn.to/3CG78ZH

channelDescription:
Hi I’m Dez!
My goal as a certified fitness and Pilates instructor is to help you experience strength and change within your body no matter your age or fitness level.
My carefully programmed workouts include tips, cues and modifications to help you get the most out of each workout while staying injury free.
With the Pilates method as my guide, I know my workouts will give you results and make you feel more powerful than ever.

SUBSCRIBE & Let's get started!
